"판 사용자 정의 <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`manage access rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` to dashboards"
msgstr "현황판에 대한 :ref:`액세스 권한 관리 <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:39
msgid ""
"centralize frequently consulted Odoo views in a personal :doc:`../../"
"applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard`"
msgstr ""
"자주 이용하는 Odoo 보기를 개인 :doc:`../../applications/productivity/"
"dashboards/my_dashboard` 에 집중적으로 모으기"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once a spreadsheet has been converted into a dashboard, it can only be "
"accessed via the Dashboards app."
msgstr ""
"스프레드시트가 현황판으로 변환되면 현황판 앱을 통해서만 액세스할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:45
msgid ""
"Unlike other Odoo dashboards, :guilabel:`My Dashboard` is not based on Odoo "
"Spreadsheet, but rather on :doc:`Odoo views <../studio/views>`."
msgstr ""
"다른 Odoo 현황판과 달리\\ :guilabel:`내 현황판`\\ 은 Odoo 스프레드시트가 아닌"
"\\ :doc:`Odoo 보기 <../studio/views>`\\ 를 기반으로 합니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:51
msgid "Use dashboards"
msgstr "현황판 사용"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:53
msgid ""
"When the Dashboards app is opened, the left panel lists all :ref:`standard, "
"pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/standard>` and :doc:`custom-built "
"dashboards <dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards>` to which a user has "
"been :ref:`granted access <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`, grouped by "
"section."
msgstr ""
"현황판 앱을 열면 왼쪽 패널에 사용자가\\ :ref:`액세스 권한이 부여된 "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`\\ 모든\\ :ref:`표준 사전 구성 현황판 "
