#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:65
msgid "Connect to the queue through Axivox"
msgstr "Axivox를 통해 대기 열에 로그인하세요"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:67
msgid ""
"Once the call queue is set up and the changes are applied, a manager can log "
