#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:155
msgid ""
"At this point, Zoiper can now make phone calls using the :abbr:`VoIP (Voice "
"over Internet Protocol)` service."
msgstr ""
"이제 Zoiper는\\ :abbr:`VoIP(Voice over Internet Protocol)`\\ 서비스를 사용하"
"여 전화를 걸 수 있습니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:None
msgid "Zoiper account setup, registration successful."
msgstr "Zoiper 계정 설정, 등록에 성공했습니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:163
msgid "Linphone"
msgstr "유선 전화"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:165
msgid ""
"Linphone is an open-source :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet "
"Protocol)` :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` softphone, used for "
"voice, video, messaging (group and individual), as well as conference calls."
msgstr ""
"Linphone은 음성, 영상, 메시징(그룹 및 개인) 및 회의 통화에 사용되는 오픈 소스"
"\\ :abbr:`VoIP(Voice over Internet Protocol)`\\ :abbr:`SIP(Session "
"Initiation Protocol)`\\ 소프트폰입니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:169
msgid ""
"To start using the Linphone app, download it to the device, via the "
"`Linphone download page <https://new.linphone.org/technical-corner/linphone?"
"qt-technical_corner=2#qt-technical_corner>`_."
msgstr ""
"Linphone 앱 사용을 시작하려면 `Linphone 다운로드 페이지<https://"
"new.linphone.org/technical-corner/linphone?qt-technical_corner=2#qt-"
"technical_corner>`_\\ 를 통해 기기에 다운로드하세요."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:172
msgid ""
"A mobile device is the most common installation, and this document covers "
"how to set up the Linphone iOS application. Screenshots and steps may differ "
"depending on the circumstances."
msgstr ""
"모바일 기기는 가장 일반적인 설치 환경이며, 이 문서는 Linphone iOS 애플리케이"
"션 설정 방법을 다룹니다. 스크린샷과 단계는 상황에 따라 다를 수 있습니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:175
msgid ""
"To begin configuring Linphone for use with a :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation "
"Protocol)` provider, first open Linphone, and an assistant screen appears."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SIP(Session Initiation Protocol)`\\ 공급자와 함께 사용하도록 Linphone"
"을 구성하기 시작하려면 먼저 Linphone을 열면 지원 화면이 나타납니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:178
msgid ""
"From this screen, select :guilabel:`Use SIP Account`. Then, on the following "
"screen, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Username`, :guilabel:`Password`, :guilabel:`Domain`, "
"and :guilabel:`Display Name`. Once complete, press :guilabel:`Login`."
msgstr ""
"이 화면에서\\ :guilabel:`SIP 계정 사용`\\ 을 선택합니다. 그런 다음 다음 화면"
"에서\\ :guilabel:`사용자 이름`,\\ :guilabel:`비밀번호`,\\ :guilabel:`도메인"
"`\\ 및\\ :guilabel:`표시 이름`\\ 을 입력합니다. 완료되면\\ :guilabel:`로그인"
"`\\ 을 누릅니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:182
msgid ""
"At this point, Linphone is ready to start making calls, once there is a "
"green button at the top of the application screen that "
"reads, :guilabel:`Connected`."
msgstr ""
"이 시점에서 애플리케이션 화면 상단에\\ :guilabel:`연결됨`\\ 이라고 표시된 녹"
"색 버튼이 있으면 Linphone은 통화를 시작할 준비가 된 것입니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:None
msgid "Linphone account setup, registration successful."
msgstr "Linphone 계정 설정, 등록에 성공했습니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:190
msgid ""
"Linphone makes a variety of applications for mobile and desktop devices in "
"operating systems, such as Windows, Linux, Apple, and Android. Because "
"Linphone is an open-source project, many new updates are released on a "
"regular basis."
msgstr ""
"Linphone은 Windows, Linux, Apple 및 Android와 같은 운영 체제에서 모바일 및 데"
"스크톱 기기를 위한 다양한 애플리케이션을 제공합니다. Linphone은 오픈 소스 프"
"로젝트이므로 많은 새로운 업데이트가 정기적으로 출시됩니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:194
msgid ""
"See `Linphone's wiki-documentation page <https://wiki.linphone.org/xwiki/"
"wiki/public/view/Linphone/>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Linphone 위키 문서 페이지 <https://wiki.linphone.org/xwiki/wiki/public/view/"
"Linphone/>`_ 를 참조하세요."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:6
msgid "Odoo Phone with DIDWW"
msgstr "Odoo 전화와 DIDWW"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:8
msgid ""
"`DIDWW <https://www.didww.com/>`_ is a global |VoIP| and |SIP| trunking "
"provider that can be set up to work with Odoo **Phone**. A DIDWW account is "
"required to use this service."
msgstr ""
"`DIDWW<https://www.didww.com/>`_\\ 는 Odoo\\ **전화번호**\\ 와 함께 작동하도"
"록 설정할 수 있는 글로벌\\ |VoIP|\\ 및\\ |SIP|\\ 트렁킹 공급자입니다. 이 서비"
"스를 사용하려면 DIDWW 계정이 필요합니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:12
msgid ""
"Before setting up an account with DIDWW, verify the following requirements:"
msgstr "DIDWW로 계정을 설정하기 전에 다음 요구 사항을 확인하세요:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:14
msgid ""
"The business phone numbers are portable to DIDWW. Some providers may be "
"unable to release the phone number due to local or regional guidelines."
msgstr ""
"비즈니스 전화번호를 DIDWW로 이전할 수 있습니다. 일부 공급자는 지역 또는 지방 "
"지침으로 인해 전화번호를 해제하지 못할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:16
msgid ""
"The locations of the company and its call recipients are covered by DIDWW "
"services."
msgstr "회사와 통화 수신자의 위치가 DIDWW 서비스 범위에 포함됩니다."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:19
msgid "Configure credentials in DIDWW"
msgstr "DIDWW에서 자격 증명 구성"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:21
msgid "Navigate to the `DIDWW Dashboard <https://my.didww.com/#/dashboard>`_."
