msgid "Group dimension values"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables.rst:306
msgid ""
"Grouping dimension values allows you to declutter your pivot table by "
"combining multiple dimension values into a single, collapsible group. This "
"can be useful, for example, for creating an :guilabel:`Others` category to "
"group less significant values and allow focus to be placed on more "
"significant data."
msgstr ""

